        The method findLimitingReagent finds the limiting reagent in a reaction.

        The method is still in development and incomplete.

        Parameters:
        details - The object contains the mass, name of several reactants. Object[x][y] where x is the list of products inputted by the user. Which is ignored cause who cares about the user lel. The y is the mass and name.
        u - The universal getter.
        Returns:
        The universal getter with limiting reagent.
        Throws:
        ReactionElementNotMatchedException - The Reaction Element was not matched.
        ElementNotFoundException - The Element wasn't found.
